snippet.textDisplay: The lockers will only lock in 4 LOW,  it is controlled electricly, and yes there is a BYPASS that will allow locking in ANY RANGE even in 2 HI. There is you tube vids on how to do it, just a jumper wire to the dash switch to make the computer think it is in 4 low. In any case it will only lock when you are moving at 10 mph or lower, and it may take 30 sec or more to engage or dis engage, works best driving slow and in a straight line. If there is stress on the axels because of tight radius turning or axels articulated it may not lock untill you are back on level and straight  line of travel.   CHEERS the trucl is looking good.                          Steve h.
